content: The timezone can be set in Settings/Calendar. Pick a city that is in the AEST zone, such as Sydney (see picture). For individual events or tasks, select Options/Show Timezones in the event or task dialog and set the zone.
creator: sfhowes

content: Setting up email accounts on Thunderbird is straightforward. Just follow the steps to add your account details, and it will automatically configure most settings. If not, manually enter the server info provided by your email provider. Easy to do!
